data_table.description: Outcomes - Clinical Trials (CT) + Observational Study (OS) Self-Reported data file. Note: The rel# in the file name is used by the submitter to track embargo releases. Files that have "rel2" or later may either contain additional variables or more recent data as compared to the previous rel#.

variable.name: F33ANGHRTHSP
variable.description: F33 Angina plus Hospitalized Heart Condition
variable.comment: This variable indicates self reported angina with hospitalization for a heart condition that may or may not be related to the angina. Only collected during the WHI Extension Study 1. This variable differs from the WHI Extension Study 2 definition of self reported angina.

variable.name: LAST33WHIDY
variable.description: Days enrollment to last WHI form 33/33D
variable.comment: LAST33WHIDY is calculated as the days from enrollment to the latest Form 33 in the WHI study. Because of the adjudication process, it is possible that there are some adjudicated events with days to event beyond LAST33WHIDY.

variable.name: LAST33EXT1DY
variable.description: Days enrollment to last Ext1 form 33/33D
variable.comment: LAST33EXT1DY is calculated as the days from enrollment to the latest Form 33 in Extension Study 1. Because of the adjudication process, it is possible that there are some adjudicated events with days to event beyond LAST33EXT1DY.
